      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for everyday commuting. The exterior shows some signs of its history, including several light scratches on the door panels and a small dent on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays some minor staining and wear consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well, though it may require routine maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a solid, functional vehicle that offers great value for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
