    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a stunner! This car has been babied since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept in truly pristine shape. It honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you want a ride that\u2019s basically brand-new without the new-car price tag, you\u2019ve gotta come see this one! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a museum-quality E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with a documented subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS bulletproofing using Beisan Systems components. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, sending power to a factory variable M differential lock. Mechanical provenance is bolstered by a proactive rod bearing replacement using VAC Motorsports coated shells. The chassis retains its original rigidity with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is felt through every corner. No pixel degradation in the cluster, flawless interior ergonomics, and a pristine undercarriage make this a definitive collector-grade specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Clean title. No accidents. Garage kept. Full service history included.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, dings, or rock chips, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the factory floor mats have been protected by all-weather liners since day one. Every electronic component, from the crisp infotainment display to the ambient lighting and advanced driver-assistance systems, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive dealership service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. It sits on a fresh set of top-tier performance tires and delivers a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle for those who settle for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect, from the unblemished exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a rigorous standard of maintenance synonymous with a private collection. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically flawless, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite you to experience a vehicle that defies its age and stands as a testament to superior care.",
      "price": 48900.0,
