      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous, showroom-ready shape! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, meticulously cared for and kept in truly pristine condition. It drives like a dream and looks just as stunning as the day it was first bought. If you've been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new car!",
      "price": 44500.0,
