    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This pristine FD3S showcases the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. Powered by the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, it delivers linear power delivery across the rev range. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, retaining its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line has been meticulously inspected to ensure the complex sequential boost transition is seamless. With an unmolested interior and original paint, this specimen offers the tactile feedback and 50/50 weight distribution exactly as Mazda intended. A collector-grade example with a documented service history.",
